Directives-- Classes
DOM--> new elements or remove elements
add new clases, attribute with elements

3 types of directives- Structural, Components,Attribute

Structural- which changes structure of DOM ngIf,ngFor

Attribute - to add or remove new behaviour of element ngStyle, ngclasses

Custom Directive
1)create a class with @Directive
2)Create an attribute directive with element ref
3) HostListener
